# PremiumTech API — VS Code REST Client / JetBrains HTTP Client
# Install "REST Client" extension in VS Code to run these directly.

@base = http://localhost:3001/api
@prod = https://premiumtech-api.onrender.com/api

### ── AUTH ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Login (admin)
POST {{base}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@premiumtech.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Login (customer)
POST {{base}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "sofia.martin@gmail.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### ── SEMANTIC SEARCH ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Natural language search
GET {{base}}/search?q=gaming+laptop+under+1000&sort=relevance&perPage=6

### Filter only (no AI)
GET {{base}}/search?category=smartphones&brand=apple&inStock=true&sort=price_asc

### Hybrid: query + filters
GET {{base}}/search?q=wireless+headphones&minPrice=50&maxPrice=300&inStock=true

### ── SIMILAR PRODUCTS ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Get similar products (replace :id with a real product id from search results)
GET {{base}}/products/PRODUCT_ID/similar

### ── AI ASSISTANT ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Response is SSE (text/event-stream). REST Client shows raw stream.

### Guest chat — product recommendation
POST {{base}}/assistant/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "I need a laptop for video editing, budget around $1500",
  "history": []
}

### Multi-turn conversation
POST {{base}}/assistant/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "Which one has more RAM?",
  "history": [
    { "role": "user",      "content": "Show me MacBook options" },
    { "role": "assistant", "content": "Here are the MacBook models available..." }
  ]
}

### Authenticated chat (add to cart) — replace TOKEN with JWT from login response
POST {{base}}/assistant/chat
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN

{
  "message": "Add the cheapest laptop to my cart",
  "history": []
}

### ── PRODUCTS ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### List products (paginated)
GET {{base}}/products?page=1&limit=12

### Product detail
GET {{base}}/products/PRODUCT_SLUG

### ── HEALTH ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Health check
GET {{base}}/health
